OL,3,CPlotting Southport-style mass casualty
OL,4,Cattacks to become criminal offence
OL,6,FPlotting Southport-style mass casualty
OL,7,Fattacks is to become a specific
OL,8,Fcriminal offence under new plans set
OL,9,Fout in the Kings Speech.
OL,11,FTerror laws watchdog Jonathan Hall KC
OL,12,Frecommended the change in March 2025
OL,13,Fafter the attack, in which three young
OL,14,Fgirls were murdered at a dance class
OL,15,Fand eight more were injured.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
