FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778753278
OL,3,CPlotting Southport-style mass casualty
OL,4,Cattacks to become criminal offence
OL,6,FQuestions were raised following the
OL,7,FSouthport attacks after the
OL,8,Fperpetrator was only charged with a
OL,9,Fterror offence in relation to
OL,10,Fpossession of ricin, and not the
OL,11,Fatrocity itself.
OL,13,FHe had been referred to the anti-
OL,14,Fextremism scheme Prevent three times,
OL,15,Fbut had his case closed due to lack of
OL,16,Fa terrorist ideology.
OL,18,FThere was a second case where a 16-
OL,19,Fyear-old had planned a primary school
OL,20,Fmassacre in Luton after killing his
OL,21,Ffamily.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778753278
OL,3,CPlotting Southport-style mass casualty
OL,4,Cattacks to become criminal offence
OL,6,FMr Hall called for a new offence to
OL,7,Fcover plotting mass casualty attacks
OL,8,Fwhich are not motivated by a terrorist
OL,9,Fideology.
OL,11,FIn March 2026, Mr Hall said the
OL,12,FGovernment needed to "get on" with
OL,13,Fmaking the change.
OL,15,FHe said: "I'm completely convinced
OL,16,Fthat my recommendation is right.
OL,26,@tD@VOUtD@]O]wD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778753278
OL,3,CPlotting Southport-style mass casualty
OL,4,Cattacks to become criminal offence
OL,6,F"I'm afraid that there is a particular
OL,7,Fway with mass casualty attacks which
OL,8,Fattracts future attackers, and that's
OL,9,Fwhy I think my recommendation is
OL,10,Fwarranted."
OL,12,FThe Bill will also criminalise the
OL,13,Fcreation and sharing of material
OL,14,Fonline that "glorifies, trivialises or
OL,15,Fnormalises serious violence".
OL,17,FThere are concerns that young
OL,18,Fteenagers are being exposed to extreme
OL,19,Fcontent, with TikTok and X being
OL,20,Fsingled out by the Government as
OL,21,F"common exposure points".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@KO]vD@MOUwD@\O]}D@AOU}D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
