PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778753278
OL,3,CPlotting Southport-style mass casualty
OL,4,Cattacks to become criminal offence
OL,6,FThe top 24 gore sites, which host
OL,7,Fmaterial including violence by
OL,8,Fcriminal cartels, beheadings and
OL,9,Fextreme animal cruelty, attract around
OL,10,Fa million visits by UK users each
OL,11,Fmonth, the Government said.
OL,13,FA total of 469 referrals to the
OL,14,Fgovernment anti-extremism scheme
OL,15,FPrevent from April 2024 to March 2025
OL,16,Fwere related to concerns over
OL,17,Ffascination with violence or mass
OL,18,Fcasualty attacks, equivalent to 5% of
OL,19,Fthe total.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
